targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  time,
  latitude AS latitude_last,
  longitude AS longitude_last,
  ground_heading_deg * 100000 AS ground_heading_deg
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  time,
  latitude,
  longitude,
  carrier_phase_range_int
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  latitude,
  horizontal_accuracy_m
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  latitude AS latitude_last,
  longitude AS longitude_last,
  ground_heading_deg * 100000 AS ground_heading_deg
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  time,
  latitude,
  longitude,
  carrier_phase_range_int
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  altitude_m,
  altitude_m + vertical_accuracy_m AS upper_bound,
  altitude_m - vertical_accuracy_m AS lower_bound
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  ground_speed_ms,
  ground_speed_ms + speed_accuracy_ms AS upper_bound,
  GREATEST(ground_speed_ms - speed_accuracy_ms, 0) AS lower_bound
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) 
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT

FROM

SELECT
  num_sats_tracked,
  num_sats_visible
FROM
  station_telemetry
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) 
ORDER BY
  time

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  time,
  id::BIGINT,
  vpn_ip,
  group_name,
  group_name as Actions,
  ping,
  ping AS ping_avg,
  ping AS ping_trend
FROM network_telemetry
WHERE $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY time ASC
